&lt;li&gt;Air does not exhaust after removal of tubing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Copper-free (Electroless nickel plated)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This product is not intended for use in potable water systems&lt;/li&gt;
